Plot: A gritty story taking place in Stockholm, about the passionate love between the self-abusive Sebastian who wants to be a woman, and the easy-going Andreas who is certainly not gay.
Title: Something Must Break
Writer: Eli Levén (screenplay), Ester Martin Bergsmark (screenplay), Lars Bang (collaboration on screenplay), Eli Levén (book)
Actors: Saga Becker, Iggy Malmborg, Shima Niavarani, Mattias Åhlén
